summary: A reskin of the female armor for the Thieves Guildleader.
descriptionHtml:
Female Thief Guild Leader v1.0
--------------

A reskin of the female armor for the Thieves Guildleader.

INSTALL
-------

Simply unzip the archive to your main Skyrim directory.

NOTES
-----

Changed the medallion on the chest. Swapped leather shoulder armor for something more metallic. Reworked the normal and specular maps to work. Changed the emblem to crossed keys on the leather shoulderpad.

Feel free to redistribute with credit.

COMING SOON in v2
-----------------

Better coloring.
Cleaner buckles.
Reworked hood.
Better specular maps.

Enjoy

 - Ludovico

ISSUES
------

Metal shoulder plate is a bit plain, this will be changed in an update.
author: Ludovico
